waveOutGetDevCapsA
timeGetTime
timeGetDevCaps
timeBeginPeriod
timeEndPeriod
mciSendStringA
mciSendStringW
mciGetErrorStringA
midiOutOpen
midiOutClose
midiOutShortMsg
midiOutGetNumDevs
joyGetNumDevs
joyGetPos
